#!/usr/bin/python -tt
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

###
###  logster
###
###  Tails a log and applies a log parser (that knows what to do with specific)
###  types of entries in the log, then reports metrics to Ganglia and/or Graphite.
###
###  Usage:
###
###    $ logster [options] parser logfile
###
###  Help:
###
###    $ logster -h
###
